snippet.title: Korix - Gameplay Trailer | PS VR
snippet.description:
Korix - Real time strategy defence for PlayStation VR.  http://www.korix.co.uk   Korix places you somewhere deep in space, fighting for your race's survival after your home world is destroyed.  With nothing left to lose you are put in the role of commander with the sole mission of taking the fight back to the enemy, showing them that you will not go down without a fight! 

(Korix - TM/ © 2016 StellarVR Limited. Developed by StellarVR Limited. All rights reserved.)
